==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: huànnàn jiàn zhēnqíng

===Etymology===
Literally: Adversity allows one to see the true feelings of others.

===Proverb===
'''[[患難]][[見]][[真情]]'''

# [[A friend in need is a friend indeed]].

===Alternate forms===
[[患难见真情]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

